[[File:Consortium_palace.jpg|thumb|right|200px|A Consortium palace]]
A '''Zann Consortium palace''' was a large building used by the [[Zann Consortium/Legends|Zann Consortium]] underworld organization. These buildings were often built on worlds with strong Consortium influence, and served as the center for Consortium monetary dealings there. The building was well-defended, making it harder for [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] or [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces to destroy it. They were also equipped with a [[Deflector shield generator/Legends|shield generator]] and a [[Communications array/Legends|communications array]]. This structure could also create [[Defiler]]s, [[Mobile Defense Unit]]s, and [[Ewok Handler]]s.

==Appearances==
